author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
What would you do if you had a perfect 3D scan of your face? In an exercise in building animatronic eyes, Adam called up Bill Doran (@punishedprops) to colloborate on a massive 3D printed head. Watch digital design merge with special effects modelmaking in this surreal build! 

Thanks so much to Bill for helping with this project! Find his work at https://www.punishedprops.com/ and @punishedprops 

Shot and edited by Josh Self
Music by Jinglepunks
